"{\"uid\": \"fortune.com-europe-2024-01-05-hotels-paris-olympics-craze-hiking-prices-opening-night-ufc-que-choisir\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"It's 2024, and that means theOlympicsare back.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 46, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the world's elite athletes ramp up their training ahead of the event in Paris, hotels are also preparing-by hiking up room prices to astronomical levels.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 125, \"end\": 130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0981740269359923e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three- and four-star hotels in Paris have tripled prices for the night of the Olympics opening ceremony on July 26, consumer interest group UFC-Que Choisir foundper its reportpublished in late December.\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0981740269359923e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC-Que_Choisir\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UFC-Que Choisir\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC-Que_Choisir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC-Que_Choisir\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UFC polled 80 hotels in total and found that prices for the night of July 26 are \\u20ac1,033 ($1,128) on average-that's up 226% from fares two weeks earlier for July 12 to July 13.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9999983545644576, \"rank\": 1.6218852765946995e-06, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In view of the Paris Olympics next summer, local hoteliers are not going in with the back of the spoon.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have literally skyrocketed their prices,\\\" UFC said.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9999983545644576, \"rank\": 1.6218852765946995e-06, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite prices running high, hotels were seeing strong demand.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Seven months ahead of the Olympics, half of the hotels contacted by the French group said they were fully booked while 30% of them had a minimum two-night requirement for bookings.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6592398323793051, \"rank\": 0.507210397183469, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With about15 millionspectators expected to come to the capital of France-a city with a population of just above 2 million-accommodation will be a hot commodity this summer.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Short-stay rental companyAirbnburged Parisians toopen up their homesfor rent to help accommodate the inflow of tourists.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That will also help place a lid on prices by increasing supply, Airbnb chief Brian Cheskytold Reutersin September.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Airbnb\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Short-term rentals will play a key role as the sector is more elastic in terms of capacity than hotels,\\\" Alexander G\\u00f6ransson, a senior consultant at Euromonitor International, added ina report.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1514, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\", \"score\": 0.9531478737919447, \"rank\": 0.04331883208689619, \"text\": \"Alexander\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris was never among Europe's cheapest destinations to visit-but it's about to get more expensive with the city's tourist tax set to triple.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0981740269359923e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At present, the tax varies from \\u20ac0.25 to \\u20ac5.5,France 24reported, which is now subject to change in the lead-up to the Olympics to support the Parisian public transport systems.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's another blow for the competitiveness of our sector as well as France's image at a time when all attention is on the Paris 2024 Olympics,\\\" hotel and restaurant union UMIH and the GNC organization of hotel chains said in a statement last month, according to the same news outlet.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1993, \"end\": 1999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999472110849108, \"rank\": 2.9019714433566836e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_National_Congress\", \"score\": 0.9992140788125256, \"rank\": 0.0007865393454939545, \"text\": \"GNC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_National_Congress\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another concern has been the thousands of migrants and others who have beenmoved fromthe French capital, exacerbating its homelessness crisis.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2299, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6592398323793051, \"rank\": 0.507210397183469, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Questions have been raised about France'spreparednessfor hosting the large-scale sporting event that attracts viewers from all over the world.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Its transport system-which connects the different zones of the city-has been front and center in the conversation, after Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo cautionedin Novemberthat parts of the transport system will not be able to meet capacity.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2630, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Public transport has been a cause for concern in recent months with abedbug outbreakand overcrowding.\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Metroticketsin the city will see a nearly 100% price hike through the period of the event, which goes on till Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet hosting an iconic eventlike the Olympicscould ultimately be good for the French capital, according to Euromonitor's G\\u00f6ransson.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3033, \"end\": 3039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6592398323793051, \"rank\": 0.507210397183469, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Assuming a successfully executed Games, it will be a great opportunity to showcase Paris as a destination,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3172, \"end\": 3177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0981740269359923e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The true benefits of a successful Paris 2024, forecast to be watched by a global television audience of 4 billion, will be felt in subsequent years.\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike during the Olympics itself, this will benefit the overall tourism economy and not just hospitality.\\\"\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prarthana Prakash was a Europe business reporter atFortune.\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3465, \"end\": 3474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Prarthana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prayer\"}, {\"begin\": 3475, \"end\": 3482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prakash_Yashwant_Ambedkar\", \"score\": 0.9999999999672582, \"rank\": 3.280891782653066e-11, \"text\": \"Prakash\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prakash_Yashwant_Ambedkar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prakash_Yashwant_Ambedkar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 Fortune Media IP Limited.\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3533, \"end\": 3540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"score\": 0.99995906779951, \"rank\": 4.0933875998225804e-05, \"text\": \"Fortune\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\"}, {\"begin\": 3547, \"end\": 3549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intellectual_property\", \"score\": 0.9859148302472124, \"rank\": 0.014282277313632049, \"text\": \"IP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intellectual_property\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intellectual_property\"}]}, {\"sentence\